CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper July 28, 1945, pg. 1, reads: "For Conspicuous Service - Frederick Holmes, labor leader and member of the Department of Public Assistance, has the Order of Salem bestowed upon him by the Rev. Howard Mather of the order of Antioch, at ceremonies in Calvary ME Church Wednesday morning. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Rev. Howard Mather of Order of Antioch facing man in doctoral robes in Calvary Methodist Episcopal (United Methodist) Church, 971 Beech Avenue, Northside
